ls `Dispatcher.RunWorkflow()` to launch container run\n  - Links child run to parent via `ParentRunID` and `TaskID`\n  - Polls via `waitForRun()` until terminal state\n  - Maps `RunStateSucceeded` → \"success\", others → \"fail\"\n\n- **executeAgent()** (lines 224-278): Runs agent commands on the host\n\nEnvironment variables injected into host steps:\n- `CLOCHE_PROJECT_DIR`: Project root\n- `CLOCHE_STEP_OUTPUT`: Path to write step output\n- `CLOCHE_PREV_OUTPUT`: Previous step's output file\n- `CLOCHE_RUN_ID`: Host run ID\n- `CLOCHE_TASK_ID`: Assigned task ID\n- `CLOCHE_MAIN_RUN_ID`: (finalize only) Run ID from main phase\n- `CLOCHE_MAIN_OUTCOME`: (finalize only) Outcome of main phase\n\n---\n\n### 6. **Domain Types**\n\n**File: `/workspace/internal/domain/workflow.go`**\n\n- **StepType** enum (lines 16-20): Includes `StepTypeWorkflow` for workflow dispatch steps\n- **WorkflowLocation** enum (lines 23-33): `LocationHost` vs `LocationContainer`\n- **knownStepConfigKeys** (lines 246-257): Includes:\n  - `workflow_name`: Name of container workflow to dispatch\n  - `prompt_step`: Override which step's output to use as prompt\n\n- **ValidateLocation()** (lines 233-242): Enforces that `workflow_name` steps only appear in host workflows\n\n**File: `/workspace/internal/domain/run.go`**\n\n- **RunState** constants: `RunStateSucceeded`, `RunStateFailed`, `RunStateCancelled`, `RunStatePending`, `RunStateRunning`\n- **Run.IsHost** flag: True for host workflow runs (set in `runNamedWorkflow()`)\n\n---\n\n### 7. **Parser Implementation**\n\n**File: `/workspace/internal/dsl/parser.go` + tests in `/workspace/internal/dsl/parser_test.go`**\n\n- **ParseAllForHost()** (line 69): Parses `.cloche/host.cloche` and returns `map[string]*domain.Workflow`\n- Supports multiple workflows in same file (list-tasks, main, finalize)\n- Infers `StepTypeWorkflow` when `workflow_name` is present in step config\n- Full test coverage in parser_test.go (lines 650-695)\n\n---\n\n### 8. **Special Handling**\n\n**Task Deduplication** (`/workspace/internal/host/loop.go`, lines 324-346):\n- Prevents reassigning the same task ID within `DedupTimeout` window (default 5 minutes)\n- Dedup entries expire automatically\n\n**Status Tracking** (`/workspace/internal/host/runner.go`, lines 196-256):\n- `hostStatusHandler` logs step events and publishes them via `LogBroadcast`\n- Enables `cloche logs` to work identically for host and container runs\n- Tracks step start/completion times and results\n\n**Daemon Startup** (`/workspace/cmd/cloched/main.go`, lines 196-234):\n- `autoRunActiveProjects()` scans projects with `active: true` config\n- Auto-executes host \"main\" workflow at daemon startup (no loop)\n\n---\n\n### 9. **Key Files Summary**\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `/workspace/.cloche/host.cloche` | DSL definitions of all three workflows |\n| `/workspace/internal/host/runner.go` | Main workflow runner, parses DSL, calls executor |\n| `/workspace/internal/host/executor.go` | Step execution (script, agent, workflow dispatch) |\n| `/workspace/internal/host/loop.go` | Three-phase orchestration loop, task deduplication, concurrency |\n| `/workspace/internal/host/task.go` | Task structure, JSON parsing, TaskAssigner interface |\n| `/workspace/internal/adapters/grpc/server.go` | Loop creation and phase function wiring |\n| `/workspace/internal/domain/workflow.go` | Workflow/step types, location validation |\n| `/workspace/cmd/cloched/main.go` | Daemon startup, auto-run for active projects |"}],"totalDurationMs":47298,"totalTokens":59989,"totalToolUseCount":23,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":5634,"cache_read_input_tokens":51919,"output_tokens":2434,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":5634},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
